net.hudup.core.data

Class MemProfiles

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hudup.core.data.MemProfiles
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, Profiles, Transfer

    public class MemProfiles
extends java.lang.Object
implements Profiles
    This class represents a collection of many profiles. It can be considered as a table or storage in memory. It implements directly the interface Profiles.
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
